Trichet Says ECB Shouldn’t Refinance Euro Member Bailouts

-- B y   G a b i   T h e s i n g
-- 
2011-10-04T14:55:49Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-04/trichet-says-ecb-shouldn-t-refinance-euro-member-bailouts.html
European Central Bank President Jean-
Claude Trichet said the ECB shouldn’t play a role in providing
funds to bail out debt-strapped nations.  “I’m not in favor of bailout funds refinanced by the
ECB,” Trichet said at a parliamentary hearing in Brussels
today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Gabi Thesing in London at 
